div:

This page provides a list of the FHIR artifacts defined as part of this implementation guide.


Knowledge Artifacts: Activity Definitions {% capture grouping_desc %}These define activities that can be performed as part of content in this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Polio Vaccination Session

            {% capture desc %}Administer bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV) to all children 0–59 months at a vaccination site.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Rapid Coverage Monitoring

            {% capture desc %}Post-campaign rapid coverage assessment at health facility catchment area level.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Supervision Visit

            {% capture desc %}Supervisory visit to monitor and support campaign execution at the district level.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





Knowledge Artifacts: Plan Definitions {% capture grouping_desc %}These define workflows, rules, strategies, or protocols as part of content in this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Polio SIA Campaign

            {% capture desc %}Campaign template for a Polio Supplementary Immunization Activity targeting children 0–59 months.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





Structures: Resource Profiles {% capture grouping_desc %}These define constraints on FHIR resources for systems conforming to this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Microplan CarePlan

            {% capture desc %}An instantiated immunization campaign for a specific geographic area and time period.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan Location

            {% capture desc %}A location in the immunization campaign hierarchy, from country down to vaccination site.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan PlanDefinition

            {% capture desc %}A campaign template that defines activities and which location hierarchy levels they target.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan Target Population

            {% capture desc %}Estimated target population for vaccination at a specific location.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan Task

            {% capture desc %}A concrete campaign activity assigned to a team at a specific location and time.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





Structures: Extension Definitions {% capture grouping_desc %}These define constraints on FHIR data types for systems conforming to this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Campaign Location

            {% capture desc %}Links a resource to a location in the campaign hierarchy.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Target Location Type

            {% capture desc %}Specifies which level of the location hierarchy a PlanDefinition action targets for Task generation.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





Terminology: Value Sets {% capture grouping_desc %}These define sets of codes used by systems conforming to this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Microplan Activity Type ValueSet

            {% capture desc %}Types of activities performed during an immunization campaign.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan Location Type ValueSet

            {% capture desc %}Administrative levels in the immunization campaign location hierarchy.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan Participant Role ValueSet

            {% capture desc %}Roles of participants in immunization campaign activities.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





Terminology: Code Systems {% capture grouping_desc %}These define new code systems used by systems conforming to this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Microplan Activity Type CodeSystem

            {% capture desc %}Types of activities performed during an immunization campaign.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan Location Type CodeSystem

            {% capture desc %}Administrative levels in the immunization campaign location hierarchy.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Microplan Participant Role CodeSystem

            {% capture desc %}Roles of participants in immunization campaign activities.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





